{"tid":2254703,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：講書店講棵菜都禁 網民鬧爆審查  fb封鎖區家麟網誌（李八方）","createTime":"2020-10-23T04:41:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-23T04:41:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"03151790cd8903bdb6c2ef0e331082ceed75e5dd","tid":2254703,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T04:41:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201023/KIPYB5OORZECRKJ7BIR5X56BKY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201023%2FKIPYB5OORZECRKJ7BIR5X56BKY%2F&d=LL0CSI02xgrrxVkOh%2Fu%2FRAogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=fd84ccd8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201023%2FKIPYB5OORZECRKJ7BIR5X56BKY%2F&h=929dea7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201023/KIPYB5OORZECRKJ7BIR5X56BKY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：講書店講棵菜都禁 網民鬧爆審查 <br />\nfb封鎖區家麟網誌（李八方）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7m_D6__2CClPtfXOEr5UJBZlLVU=/1400x910/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VFVL2KDCORFJ5GBSAXMNVLAUHU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7m_D6__2CClPtfXOEr5UJBZlLVU%3D%2F1400x910%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVFVL2KDCORFJ5GBSAXMNVLAUHU.gif&h=04190f19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■傳媒人區家麟網誌慘被fb封鎖，原因不明。<br />\n<br />\n以往經常有民主派人士投訴俾facebook、YouTube禁言或者黃標，呢個情況似乎越嚟越嚴重，連言論溫和嘅非建制人士都中招，今次受害人係資深傳媒人區家麟，佢嘅網誌《潮池》無端端俾facebook封鎖，而被封嘅原因竟然可能因為「一棵菜與幾本書」？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/gh395JdS7dAZZmmjNuWUPu5o5Uk=/1457x954/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BX5VKUNA2BEUPDZGMA6QFRWRGY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fgh395JdS7dAZZmmjNuWUPu5o5Uk%3D%2F1457x954%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBX5VKUNA2BEUPDZGMA6QFRWRGY.jpg&h=6ba90214&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■fb唔畀用戶分享《潮池》連結，之後又偷偷地解封。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/nDAoXJK3_54h1-ie1zu-Az9SZzw=/1396x1396/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/L3JEN2G25FEXJFQYECDSD5CGVU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FnDAoXJK3_54h1-ie1zu-Az9SZzw%3D%2F1396x1396%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FL3JEN2G25FEXJFQYECDSD5CGVU.jpg&h=f63890fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■薯伯伯fb早前都被禁言，懷疑同泰國示威帖文有關。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔會解釋 賴演算法<br />\n<br />\n區家麟噚日寫文講返成件事，八方睇完都覺荒謬。佢話前日突然收到facebook通知，話封鎖咗佢網誌一篇講樓上書店嘅文章，篇文章內容係講書店賣乜書以及深水埗文化，但被fb以「Abusive」為由封鎖。通常被fb用以abusive為由封鎖嘅資訊可能係啲相出事，但區家麟話文章配圖只係一棵菜同幾本書，究竟一棵菜加幾本書有幾abusive呢？<br />\n<br />\n之後fb連佢關於王婆婆嘅文章、。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n呢件事好快引起網民關注，有。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n有份揭露區家麟俾facebook搞嘅旅遊寫作人「薯伯伯」，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n李八方"}]}